<p>The <b>Bible code</b>, also known as the <b>Torah code</b>, is a <a href="/wiki/Cipher" title="Cipher">cipher</a> alleged to exist within the texts, that when decoded form words and phrases supposedly demonstrating foreknowledge and prophecy. The study and results from this cipher have been popularized by the book <i><a href="/wiki/The_Bible_Code_(book)" title="The Bible Code (book)">The Bible Code</a></i>.</p>
