<li id="cite_note-cnn-40">^ <a href="#cite_ref-cnn_40-0" title=""><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-cnn_40-1" title=""><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9706/04/israel.bible/drosninlog.html" class="external text" title="http://www.cnn.com/WORLD/9706/04/israel.bible/drosninlog.html" rel="nofollow">CNN - Meet Michael Drosnin Author, "The Bible Code"</a></li>
</ol>
</div>
